Introduction

Jinjin & Rocky (Korean: 진진과 로키; Japanese: ジンジンとロッキー) is the second sub-unit of the boy group ASTRO from Fantagio Music. They made their official debut on January 17, 2022, with their first mini-album "Restore".

On April 19, 2023, Fantagio announced the exit of Rocky, after his contract expired, thus ending the duo subunit.
